      <div type="commentary" xml:lang="en">
	<p>This edition is based on <ref target="bibl:Sarma1993">Sarma and Varaprasada Rao 1993</ref>.</p>
	<p><ref target="bibl:NagarajaRao1985">Nagaraja Rao</ref> followed the reading of <ref target="bibl:ARIE1968">ARIE</ref> and understood this inscription to refer to a woman from Simhala (Sihaḷī). However, as J. Varaprasada Rao noted, this is a proper name.</p>
      </div>
